The paper focuses on the utilization of big data and IoT services, which involves machine learning methods (cs.LG) and resource management design (cs.CE). The paper also discusses economic modeling and analysis, which falls under information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography and security (cs.CR). Finally, the paper deals with complex system operations, which can be categorized under distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
